It is recommended that the Municipality considers the following:

Device the sworn statement form to facilitate compliance of the taxpayer on the declaration of revenue in obtaining business permit and residence certificate;

Review certain provisions on the practicality of its implementation and if could not be implemented, consider amending the Code;

Adopt proper and clear procedure on how to implement certain provision of the code;

Review the policy of requiring slaughtering of animals for public consumption only to the slaughterhouse in the absence of a Municipal Slaughterhouse; and

Conduct proper public information in case the un-implemented provision of the Code will be implemented.

